          <div class="bg-zinc-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-600 p-8 my-10 reveal">
            <h4 class="text-zinc-900 font-bold mb-2">Cabinet Builder Pro-Tip:</h4>
            <p class="italic">"Wire shelving flexes under load and leaves grid marks on folded clothing. Our furniture-grade plywood shelves are solid, smooth, and adjustable on Hafele standards — reposition them without tools as your wardrobe changes. That adaptability is why our closet systems last decades while wire racks get ripped out within five years."</p>
          </div>

          <section class="reveal">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4">Custom Closet Built-Ins Near You</h2>
            <p>
              We build custom closet systems for homeowners throughout the Temecula Valley. Whether you're in Bear Creek, Greer Ranch, or Copper Canyon in Murrieta, or nearby cities, our shop is centrally located for fast turnaround and responsive service.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6">
