            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="reveal">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4">Related Services</h2>
            <p>
              Our closet built-ins use the same materials and craftsmanship as our <a href="/services/custom-kitchen-cabinets" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">custom kitchen cabinets</a> and <a href="/services/bathroom-remodeling" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">bathroom vanities</a>. Many homeowners match their closet system to existing cabinetry throughout the home — same door style, same finish, same hardware — for a cohesive whole-home aesthetic. See our full range of services at <a href="/services" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">First Class WoodWorks Services</a>.
            </p>
          </section>

        </div>

